Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game
class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Checks which entity the current entity is bound to as slave.

Usage
-----

*entity* getBindMaster()

Parameters
----------

This script event does not accept parameters.

Examples
--------

    $my_entity.getBindMaster();

Notes
-----

Not available.

